\end{figure}

   The quark propagators computed from the diagrams of Fig.~\ref{fig:Omega1} are also used now for the diagrams of
Fig.~\ref{fig:Omega0}. Though one looses self-consistency, this approximation is still consistent with $N_c$ counting~\cite{Hufner:1994ma,Zhuang:1994dw,Oertel:2000cw}. 
